	#include<iostream>
	#include<cstdio>
	
	 int x1,y1,x2,y2,x3,y3,x4,y4,p,q,r,s;

	int main(){
		int test;
		scanf("%d",&test);
		while(test--){
			scanf("%d %d %d %d",&x1,&y1,&x2,&y2);
			scanf("%d %d %d %d",&x3,&y3,&x4,&y4);
			if(x3>x1)p=x3;else p=x1;
			if(y3>y1)q=y3;else q=y1;
			if(x4<x2)r=x4;else r=x2;
			if(y4<y2)s=y4;else s=y2;
			if((p<r)&&(q<s))
				printf("%d %d %d %d\n",p,q,r,s);
				else printf("No Overlap\n");
			}
		return 0;
		}
